   <p xml:id="124" begin="00:03:14.467" end="00:03:17.036">YOU ABOUT IT WOULD YOU</p>
   <p xml:id="125" begin="00:03:15.902" end="00:03:17.870">PLEASE REMOVE YOUR FOOT FROM</p>
   <p xml:id="126" begin="00:03:17.169" end="00:03:19.505">MY DOOR?</p>
   <p xml:id="127" begin="00:03:18.004" end="00:03:20.006">&gt;&gt; YOU MADE A LOT OF PEOPLE</p>
   <p xml:id="128" begin="00:03:19.639" end="00:03:21.407">VERY UPSET.</p>
   <p xml:id="129" begin="00:03:20.139" end="00:03:22.208">I THINK YOU OWE THE COUNTRY</p>
   <p xml:id="130" begin="00:03:21.541" end="00:03:26.512">AN EXPLANATION.</p>
   <p xml:id="131" begin="00:03:22.341" end="00:03:27.780">&gt;&gt; YOU ARE GIVING SPEECHES.</p>
   <p xml:id="132" begin="00:03:26.646" end="00:03:28.514">&gt;&gt; JESSE WATTERS JOINS US</p>
   <p xml:id="133" begin="00:03:27.914" end="00:03:29.515">NOW FROM BOSTON.</p>
   <p xml:id="134" begin="00:03:28.648" end="00:03:30.283">I THOUGHT YOU HANDLED THAT</p>
   <p xml:id="135" begin="00:03:29.649" end="00:03:30.716">WELL WITH THE GUY.</p>
   <p xml:id="136" begin="00:03:30.416" end="00:03:31.984">&gt;&gt; THANK YOU.</p>
   <p xml:id="137" begin="00:03:30.850" end="00:03:33.786">&gt;&gt; IT'S THE SAME OLD STUFF.</p>
   <p xml:id="138" begin="00:03:32.118" end="00:03:34.120">YOU KNOW, THESE GUYS ARE</p>
   <p xml:id="139" begin="00:03:33.920" end="00:03:35.421">COWARDS.</p>
   <p xml:id="140" begin="00:03:34.253" end="00:03:36.889">HE IS A COWARD.</p>
   <p xml:id="141" begin="00:03:35.555" end="00:03:37.290">HE HAD THE COURAGE OF HIS</p>
   <p xml:id="142" begin="00:03:37.023" end="00:03:38.758">CONVICTIONS.</p>
   <p xml:id="143" begin="00:03:37.423" end="00:03:42.095">HE WOULD STAND UP WITH YOU</p>
   <p xml:id="144" begin="00:03:38.891" end="00:03:43.096">AND SAY THIS WHY DID I IT.</p>
