   <p xml:id="147" begin="00:03:43.963" end="00:03:45.898">IN A PLIGHT WAY.</p>
   <p xml:id="148" begin="00:03:45.198" end="00:03:47.900">YOU WERE POLITE TO HIM.</p>
   <p xml:id="149" begin="00:03:46.032" end="00:03:48.234">IS HE A VILLAIN AND A</p>
   <p xml:id="150" begin="00:03:48.034" end="00:03:50.236">COWARD.</p>
   <p xml:id="151" begin="00:03:48.368" end="00:03:52.338">THIS IS HISTORICALLY A VERY,</p>
   <p xml:id="152" begin="00:03:50.370" end="00:03:53.439">I THINK, AM HERS,</p>
   <p xml:id="153" begin="00:03:52.472" end="00:03:54.674">MASSACHUSETTS IS THE MOST</p>
   <p xml:id="154" begin="00:03:53.573" end="00:03:55.008">FAR LEFT PLACE IN THE</p>
   <p xml:id="155" begin="00:03:54.808" end="00:03:55.842">COUNTRY.</p>
   <p xml:id="156" begin="00:03:55.141" end="00:03:57.443">EVEN WORSE THAN OAKLAND.</p>
   <p xml:id="157" begin="00:03:55.975" end="00:03:59.879">&gt;&gt; IT'S EXTREMELY FAR LEFT.</p>
   <p xml:id="158" begin="00:03:57.577" end="00:04:01.714">THEY ARE A SANCTUARY CITY.</p>
