   <p xml:id="160" begin="00:04:01.848" end="00:04:08.054">TO IMPEACH GEORGE W. BUSH.</p>
   <p xml:id="161" begin="00:04:05.451" end="00:04:10.857">AND AS YOU SAW THEY FLY THE</p>
